stance measurement and the hybrid of the deep learning\nmodels with other traditional models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Aug 2016 02:49:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Aug 2016 12:51:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 8 Oct 2016 04:33:02 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 7 Jun 2017 04:34:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-08"}
